{
  "text": "The relations (4.4) and (4.5) are the rhombus rules defining the qd algorithm. 1 [CITATION_1] suggested to write down the quantities e 1 = s \u03bd+1 /s \u03bd the rhombus rules allow us to build up the qd scheme from the first column:",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "121150213"
